ed for Ireland that year,Phoebe Blair-WhiteandHilda Wallis, took part in the singles and doubles tennis.\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5311, \"end\": 5318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999163387692, \"rank\": 8.341394824167468e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 5329, \"end\": 5335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Halliwell\", \"score\": 0.7678681138415824, \"rank\": 0.3023069727085163, \"text\": \"Phoebe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Halliwell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Halliwell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only two women\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5293}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 5369, \"to\": 5373}, {\"ngram\": \"the singles\", \"from\": 5377, \"to\": 5388}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 5401, \"to\": 5407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tennis players, the water polo team, the boxers, who were mostly in the National Army and those who took part in the athletics events did not manage to secure any medals.\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5494, \"end\": 5498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Army\", \"score\": 0.9999815523625263, \"rank\": 1.843516665966911e-05, \"text\": \"Army\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Army\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Army\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tennis players\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5427}, {\"ngram\": \"the water polo team\", \"from\": 5429, \"to\": 5448}, {\"ngram\": \"the boxers\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5460}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 5518, \"to\": 5522}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletics events\", \"from\": 5526, \"to